OL,3,CPaul Clark: Military heroes and the
OL,4,Cstories they tell
OL,6,FThe term is famously associated with
OL,7,Fthe departure of Patrick Sarsfield's
OL,8,FJacobite army following the Treaty of
OL,9,FLimerick - just over a year after The
OL,10,FBattle of the Boyne in 1690.
OL,12,FNor was it uncommon for Mayo men to be
OL,13,Ffighting on opposing sides.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
