OL,3,CPaul Clark: Military heroes and the
OL,4,Cstories they tell
OL,6,FJohn MacBride, born in Westport and
OL,7,Feducated in Belfast, raised the Irish
OL,8,FTransvaal Brigade, fighting on the
OL,9,Fside of the Boers.
OL,11,FHe was executed by firing squad
OL,12,Ffollowing The Easter Rising, in 1916.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, in 1920, soldiers in the
OL,15,FConnaught Rangers, based in India,
OL,16,Fmutinied because martial law was
OL,17,Fimposed on Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
