OL,3,CPaul Clark: Military heroes and the
OL,4,Cstories they tell
OL,6,FIn 2016, a film was made about the
OL,7,Fsiege. It starred Jamie Dornan.
OL,9,FNoel Carey lives in Mayo, and is now
OL,10,Falmost 90. Standing ramrod straight,
OL,11,Fhe spoke eloquently about that battle
OL,12,F65 years ago, and, without a note!
OL,14,FCommander Ron Howko is from Michigan
OL,15,Fand served in the US army for 27
OL,16,Fyears. For almost 30 years, he has
OL,17,Fbeen a member of the American Legion
OL,18,FBranch in Co Mayo.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
