OL,3,CPaul Clark: Military heroes and the
OL,4,Cstories they tell
OL,6,FHe reminded us of Patrick Gallagher
OL,7,Ffrom Ballyhaunis, who was killed
OL,8,Fduring the Vietnam War. He emigrated
OL,9,Fto the United States at the age of 18.
OL,10,FHe was drafted into the US Marines,
OL,11,Fand killed in an ambush in 1967.
OL,13,FThree years ago the American Navy
OL,14,Fnamed a ship in his memory - USS
OL,15,FPatrick Gallagher. It is expected to
OL,16,Fmake a courtesy call to Co Mayo, later
OL,17,Fthis year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
