OL,3,CPaul Clark: Military heroes and the
OL,4,Cstories they tell
OL,6,FIn 2008 Royal Marine Robert McKibben
OL,7,Fwas killed with a colleague, while
OL,8,Fserving in Helmand Province,
OL,9,FAfghanistan.
OL,11,FIt was a sign of the changing times in
OL,12,FIreland that his military funeral
OL,13,Fcould take place in Westport.
OL,15,FThe hearse waited outside the local
OL,16,FChurch, opposite a memorial to Captain
OL,17,FJohn MacBride, executed for his part
OL,18,Fin the Easter Rising.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
