OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778094687
OL,3,CPaul Clark: Military heroes and the
OL,4,Cstories they tell
OL,6,FAncient enmities were forgotten as the
OL,7,FRoyal Marines carried his coffin
OL,8,Fthrough the streets and out to
OL,9,FAughavale Cemetery.
OL,11,FCo-incidentally, Robert McKibben is
OL,12,Fnot the only British soldier to be
OL,13,Fburied in this graveyard. Cornelius
OL,14,FCoghlan, a member of the Connaught
OL,15,FRangers, was awarded the Victoria
OL,16,FCross during the Indian Mutiny in 1857.
OL,18,FWhen he died in 1915, the political
OL,19,Fclimate in Ireland was changing. His
OL,20,Fgrave was unmarked until 2004.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
