OL,3,CPaul Clark: Military heroes and the
OL,4,Cstories they tell
OL,6,FA new headstone was dedicated by the
OL,7,Fthen Irish Minister for Defence,
OL,8,FMichael Smith. I covered the occasion
OL,9,Ffor UTV News.
OL,11,FI was back in Castlebar - for UTV News
OL,12,F- in October 2008, when the Irish
OL,13,FPresident, Mary McAleese, dedicated
OL,14,Fthe Mayo Peace Park Garden of
OL,15,FRemembrance. It commemorates all those
OL,16,Fwho served and died in the world wars,
OL,17,Fand major conflicts of the past
OL,18,Fcentury, as well as in other wars and
OL,19,Fconflicts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
