OL,3,CPaul Clark: Military heroes and the
OL,4,Cstories they tell
OL,6,FThe most uncomfortable part of the
OL,7,Fday, for me, was to listen to the
OL,8,Ffinal speaker. Michael Feeney is the
OL,9,Ffounder of the Mayo Peace Park.
OL,11,FSince its dedication, it has
OL,12,Fexperienced severe subsidence.
OL,14,FThere have been reports indicating
OL,15,Fthat the main memorial wall is
OL,16,Ftilting, cracking, and threatening to
OL,17,Fcollapse. Repairs are estimated to be
OL,18,Fcostly.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
